text: Connor McAliskey is a Gaelic football player who plays at inter-county level for Tyrone. At club level McAliskey plays for Clonoe. He started at corner- forward for Tyrone in the 2018 All-Ireland Final defeat to Dublin. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Tyrone inter-county Gaelic footballers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
